<center><b><big><big>An Example Exponential Approximation</big></big></b></center>
<br/>
<b><big><a name="Syntax" id="Syntax">Syntax</a></big></b>

<br/>
<code><font color="blue"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>#&#xA0;include&#xA0;&quot;ExpApx.hpp&quot;</span></font></code>
<code><span style='white-space: nowrap'><br/>
